<ul><li>A&nbsp;<b>voltmeter</b>&nbsp;connected directly across the terminals of the cell to measure <b>terminal pd</b>.</li><li>An&nbsp;<b>ammeter</b>&nbsp;is used to measure the&nbsp;<b>cell current</b>.</li><li>A&nbsp;<b>variable resistor</b>&nbsp;to adjust the current.</li><li>A&nbsp;<b>fixed resistor</b>&nbsp;to&nbsp;<b>limit the maximum current</b>&nbsp;that can pass through the cell.</li></ul>